From bb4205db375cc17694818cbb88f03dc039a805ce Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Marios Trivyzas <matriv@gmail.com>
Date: Thu, 12 Jun 2025 17:17:08 +0300
Subject: [PATCH] Fix aggregation on PARTITION BY cols

When a column is the PARTITION BY clause of a table we cannot use
doc values aggregators, otherwise the agg function will always return
`NULL` since no values are collected for those columns. Add checks to
`getDocValueAggregator()` to return `null` if the column has `PARTITION`
granularity.

Fixes: #17980
